(1, 'The Power of Your Subconscious', 'Joseph Murphy', '2023-08-09', 25.00, 'cover1.png', NULL, NULL, 'The Power of Your Subconscious Mind is one of the most promising self improvement books that you can gift to yourself or your loved ones. This book is designed to help you improve your relationships, health, and also to give you an internal strength that makes every hurdle look small. The book brings together best of both the worlds – scientific research as well as spiritual wisdom. It used the combined ideas to explain how our subconscious mind has the power to change our lives. The book explains how by understanding and learning to control our subconscious mind, we can welcome a world of prosperity, happiness and success. This book will act as a guide and help you understand the depth of your subconscious, get rid of fears and attract what you desire simply by changing your beliefs.', 'Introduction:\r\nIn a world dominated by external distractions, the untapped potential of our subconscious mind often remains hidden beneath the surface. \"The Power of Your Subconscious Mind Unleashed\" embarks on a journey to uncover the latent abilities within us, offering a guide to harnessing this inner strength for personal growth, success, and fulfillment.\r\n\r\nUnderstanding the Subconscious Landscape:\r\nAt the core of our being lies the subconscious mind, an intricate realm that shapes our thoughts, emotions, and actions. This chapter delves into the mechanics of the subconscious, highlighting its symbiotic relationship with conscious thought processes.\r\n\r\nNurturing Empowering Beliefs:\r\nOur beliefs, often formed early in life, exert a profound influence on our subconscious programming. By recognizing and altering limiting beliefs, we can pave the way for transformative change, allowing our subconscious mind to align with our aspirations.\r\n\r\nThe Art of Affirmations and Visualization:\r\nPositive affirmations and visualization techniques are potent tools for reprogramming the subconscious. This chapter explores how crafting and consistently affirming positive statements can reshape our subconscious thought patterns, ultimately driving us toward our goals.\r\n\r\nReprogramming Through Techniques:\r\nVarious techniques, from autosuggestion to meditation, can facilitate subconscious reprogramming. Through real-world examples and step-by-step guidance, readers can learn how to leverage these methods to effect lasting change.\r\n\r\nEmotional Mastery and Subconscious Alignment:\r\nEmotions hold a deep connection to the subconscious. This chapter examines strategies for understanding and channeling emotions, enabling readers to forge a harmonious relationship between their conscious and subconscious selves.\r\n\r\nFostering Fulfilling Relationships:\r\nOur subconscious beliefs significantly impact our interactions and relationships. By uncovering and reshaping these beliefs, we can cultivate healthier connections and deeper bonds with others.\r\n\r\nAligning Subconscious Power with Goals:\r\nThe synergy between conscious goals and subconscious programming can propel us to new heights. This chapter offers practical insights into harmonizing these two aspects, amplifying our ability to achieve our desires.\r\n\r\nIgniting Creative Expression:\r\nThe subconscious is a wellspring of creativity waiting to be tapped. Through exploration and techniques, readers can tap into this innate resource to enhance their creative endeavors.\r\n\r\nResilience in the Face of Challenges:\r\nAdversity is a part of life, and our subconscious responses play a pivotal role in how we navigate challenges. By cultivating resilience through subconscious conditioning, we can transform obstacles into stepping stones.\r\n\r\nEmbracing an Empowered Life:\r\nThis final chapter weaves together the wisdom and practices discussed throughout the book, presenting a comprehensive approach to living an empowered life. Readers will discover how to integrate subconscious work into their daily routines and continue their journey of self-discovery.\r\n\r\nConclusion: Unleash Your Infinite Potential\r\nAs we conclude \"The Power of Your Subconscious Mind Unleashed,\" the true extent of our capabilities becomes clear. The book underscores the profound impact of the subconscious on every facet of our existence and empowers readers to embark on a path of conscious transformation. By tapping into the wellspring of potential within, we open doors to a life defined by purpose, accomplishment, and unbounded joy. The journey to self-empowerment begins now.', 'Motivational'),
(3, 'Ikigai - A Long and Happy Life', 'Francesc Miralles', '2016-08-17', 20.00, 'cover2.jpg', NULL, NULL, '\"Discover the profound wisdom of \'Kigai\' as it unveils simple yet impactful secrets for a joyful, purposeful, and enduring life. Through a seamless integration of science-backed insights and candid, empathetic dialogue, this book becomes an irresistible page-turner. Neil Pasricha, renowned author of \'The Happiness Equation,\' praises its gentle approach, inviting readers on a transformative journey of self-discovery. With warmth, patience, and compassion, \'Kigai\' empowers you to embrace a life of fulfillment, steering you with gentle nudges instead of forceful pushes. Prepare to be captivated by its compelling blend of research and relatability, as you uncover the keys to longevity and happiness. A must-read guide for anyone seeking a meaningful and contented existence.Warm, patient, and kind, this book pulls you gently along your own journey rather.', '\"Discover the profound wisdom of \'Kigai\' as it unveils simple yet impactful secrets for a joyful, purposeful, and enduring life. Through a seamless integration of science-backed insights and candid, empathetic dialogue, this book becomes an irresistible page-turner. Neil Pasricha, renowned author of \'The Happiness Equation,\' praises its gentle approach, inviting readers on a transformative journey of self-discovery. With warmth, patience, and compassion, \'Kigai\' empowers you to embrace a life of fulfillment, steering you with gentle nudges instead of forceful pushes. Prepare to be captivated by its compelling blend of research and relatability, as you uncover the keys to longevity and happiness. A must-read guide for anyone seeking a meaningful and contented existence.In a world often bustling with noise and distractions, \"Kigai\" stands as a beacon of wisdom, guiding readers towards a more meaningful and contented existence. Drawing upon a harmonious blend of ancient insights and modern scientific understanding, this captivating book unravels the art of living a life imbued with purpose and joy.\r\n\r\nThrough its engaging narrative, \"Kigai\" skillfully navigates the complexities of our fast-paced lives, offering a refreshing perspective on how to find balance and fulfillment. The author\'s empathetic dialogue creates a unique bond with readers, making the journey of self-discovery feel like an intimate conversation with a trusted friend.\r\n\r\nRenowned author Neil Pasricha, celebrated for his work on happiness and well-being, applauds \"Kigai\" for its gentle yet powerful approach. The book\'s pages turn effortlessly, revealing a treasure trove of insights that are both profound and accessible. With each chapter, readers are invited to explore the depths of their own desires, values, and aspirations, guided by the book\'s unwavering commitment to authenticity and compassion.\r\n\r\nAt the heart of \"Kigai\" lies an invitation to embrace change with open arms, to welcome personal growth not through forceful pushes, but through gentle nudges that resonate with the rhythm of one\'s own life. As readers embark on this transformative journey, they discover that the pursuit of longevity and happiness is not a distant dream, but a tangible reality waiting to be unlocked.\r\n\r\n\"Kigai\" weaves together threads of research and relatability, seamlessly blending timeless wisdom with cutting-edge scientific findings. It empowers readers to make informed choices that align with their deepest values, helping them craft a life that is uniquely their own.\r\n\r\nIn a world inundated with self-help advice, \"Kigai\" rises above the rest, offering a must-read guide for anyone seeking to navigate life\'s complexities with grace, intention, and resilience. Through its pages, readers will find a roadmap to not only enduring happiness but also a profound sense of purpose—a roadmap that has the power to transform lives and create lasting positive change.\r\n', 'Motivational'),
(4, 'The Psychology Of Money Time', 'Morgan Housel', '2023-07-06', 20.00, 'cover3.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'Timeless lessons on wealth, greed, and happiness doing well with money isn?t necessarily about what you know. It?s about how you behave. And behavior is hard to teach, even to really smart people. How to manage money, invest it, and make business decisions are typically considered to involve a lot of mathematical calculations, where data and formulae tell us exactly what to do. But in the real world, people don?t make financial decisions on a spreadsheet. They make them at the dinner table, or in a meeting room, where personal history, your unique view of the world, ego, pride, marketing, and odd incentives are scrambled together. In the psychology of money, the author shares 19 short stories exploring the strange ways people think about money and teaches you how to make better sense of one of life?s most important matters.', '\"The Psychology of Money: Unraveling the Emotional Tapestry of Wealth\" delves deep into the intricate relationship between our minds and our finances, revealing the complex interplay of emotions, beliefs, and behaviors that shape our financial journey. This book offers a thought-provoking exploration of how our psychological makeup influences our financial decisions and ultimately shapes our financial well-being.\r\n\r\nFrom the very beginning, readers are invited to explore the roots of their financial mindset. The book delves into the psychology behind money, investigating how our early experiences, societal influences, and cultural norms mold our beliefs about wealth, success, and abundance. By understanding these origins, readers can gain insight into their own financial attitudes and biases.\r\n\r\n\"The Psychology of Money\" doesn\'t just focus on numbers and strategies; it dives into the emotional currents that often steer our financial ship. It examines the powerful role that emotions like fear, greed, and contentment play in our financial choices. By recognizing these emotional triggers, readers can cultivate a heightened sense of self-awareness and make more deliberate and rational financial decisions.\r\n\r\nThrough captivating narratives and real-life case studies, the book illustrates how our behavioral patterns can either hinder or propel our financial success. It explores the phenomenon of impulse spending, the allure of instant gratification, and the pitfalls of trying to \"keep up with the Joneses.\" By dissecting these behaviors, readers can gain practical strategies for curbing impulsive spending and fostering healthier financial habits.\r\n\r\nThe book also scrutinizes the concept of risk and our ability to tolerate it. It investigates the ways in which our risk tolerance is tied to our emotional responses, shedding light on why some individuals are comfortable with investing while others shy away from it. Readers are empowered to embrace a nuanced understanding of risk and make informed investment decisions aligned with their own psychological makeup.\r\n\r\nCentral to the book\'s narrative is the idea of \"money stories\" – the deeply ingrained narratives we hold about money and its role in our lives. \"The Psychology of Money\" guides readers through a process of uncovering and reframing these narratives, empowering them to create healthier and more empowering money stories that support their financial goals.\r\n\r\nThroughout the pages of this book, readers will discover the transformative potential of mindful financial practices. By embracing mindfulness techniques, readers can develop a heightened awareness of their financial choices, break free from impulsive behaviors, and make decisions that align with their long-term financial well-being.\r\n\r\nIn the end, \"The Psychology of Money: Unraveling the Emotional Tapestry of Wealth\" serves as a guiding light for those seeking a deeper understanding of their financial relationship. It underscores the undeniable link between psychology and finance, highlighting the importance of cultivating a healthy financial mindset and making decisions that lead to lasting prosperity and peace of mind. By unraveling the emotional complexities surrounding money, readers are empowered to rewrite their financial narratives and embark on a more fulfilling and enlightened financial journey.', 'Motivational'),
(5, 'Master Your Emotions Overcome', 'Kerry J Donovan', '2023-05-11', 25.00, 'cover4.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'Want to overcome your negative feelings? Feel like you aren’t good enough? Need help dealing with stress? The solution to deal with negative emotions is to understand how your emotions work and apply specific techniques to ensure you manage them as effectively as possible. Master Your Emotions is the ‘how-to’ manual your parents should have given you at birth. By reading it, you’ll learn how to deal with negative emotions so you can live a happier, more fulfilling life. In this book, you’ll learn: • A simple formula to reprogram your mind so that you experience more positive emotions • 31 simple coping strategies to deal with negative emotions • How to change your story to take better control over your life • Practical exercises to deal with stress, defensiveness, jealousy, fear, and other negative emotions • How to use your emotions to boost your personal growth •  ', 'Introduction:\r\nIn the dynamic tapestry of human experience, emotions play a pivotal role, shaping our perceptions, actions, and interactions. \"Master Your Emotions: Navigating the Inner Landscape for Balance and Fulfillment\" invites you to embark on a transformative journey toward understanding, harnessing, and mastering your emotional world. Through insights, strategies, and practical wisdom, this book empowers you to cultivate emotional intelligence and pave the way to a more harmonious and fulfilling life.\r\n\r\nEmbracing Emotional Awareness:\r\nThe journey begins with a deep dive into the realm of emotions. Discover the spectrum of human feelings, from joy and love to fear and sadness. Learn to identify and label your emotions, unraveling the intricate threads that weave the fabric of your inner world.\r\n\r\nThe Power of Emotional Intelligence:\r\nUncover the profound impact of emotional intelligence on every facet of your life. Explore how self-awareness, self-regulation, empathy, and social skills contribute to healthier relationships, effective communication, and overall well-being.\r\n\r\nNavigating the Waves of Change:\r\nLife is an ever-changing sea, and emotions are its waves. Discover strategies to gracefully navigate the tides of change, whether it\'s dealing with transitions, challenges, or unexpected turns. Embrace adaptability as a cornerstone of emotional mastery.\r\n\r\nTransforming Negative Patterns:\r\nDelve into the art of transforming negative emotional patterns. Explore techniques to reframe your perspectives, challenge limiting beliefs, and cultivate resilience. Witness how embracing positivity can reshape your emotional landscape.\r\n\r\nHarnessing the Gift of Mindfulness:\r\nEmbark on a journey of mindfulness—a practice that anchors you in the present moment. Learn how mindfulness fosters emotional clarity, reduces reactivity, and enables you to make conscious choices in alignment with your values.\r\n\r\nThe Dance of Empathy and Compassion:\r\nUnveil the transformative power of empathy and compassion. Understand the dynamics of human connection and how empathy nurtures deeper relationships. Cultivate self-compassion to foster a nurturing relationship with yourself.\r\n\r\nCommunication as Emotional Alchemy:\r\nCommunication is a bridge between hearts, and mastering it can be an alchemical process. Discover the nuances of effective communication, from active listening to assertive expression, as you build bridges of understanding.\r\n\r\nEmbracing Vulnerability and Authenticity:\r\nExplore the liberating path of embracing vulnerability and authenticity. Understand how opening up can lead to deeper connections and emotional liberation, allowing you to show up in the world as your true self.\r\n\r\nHarmony in Relationships:\r\nNavigate the emotional intricacies of relationships—intimate, familial, and social. Learn how to navigate conflicts, set healthy boundaries, and cultivate emotional intimacy for more fulfilling connections.\r\n\r\nSustaining Your Emotional Wellbeing:\r\nSustaining emotional well-being requires ongoing care. Explore practices that nourish your emotional landscape, from self-care rituals to cultivating gratitude, ensuring a steady foundation for lasting fulfillment.\r\n\r\nConclusion: The Journey Continues:\r\nAs you conclude your exploration of mastering emotions, remember that this journey is an ongoing process. The wisdom and insights gained here are keys to unlocking a life marked by emotional equilibrium, resilience, and genuine contentment. Armed with newfound understanding and tools, you are now equipped to navigate the ebb and flow of emotions, creating a legacy of emotional mastery that resonates within you and ripples out into the world. Your journey has just begun.', 'Motivational'),
(6, 'The Unstable One Mike McCrary', ' Mike McCrary', '2019-08-14', 15.00, 'cover5.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'Discover the profound wisdom of \'Kigai\' as it unveils simple yet impactful secrets for a joyful, purposeful, and enduring life. Through a seamless integration of science-backed insights and candid, empathetic dialogue, this book becomes an irresistible page-turner. Neil Pasricha, renowned author of \'The Happiness Equation,\' praises its gentle approach, inviting readers on a transformative journey of self-discovery. With warmth, patience, and compassion, \'Kigai\' empowers you to embrace a life of fulfillment, steering you with gentle nudges instead of forceful pushes. Prepare to be captivated by its compelling blend of research and relatability, as you uncover the keys to longevity and happiness. A must-read guide for anyone seeking a meaningful and contented existence.Warm, patient, and kind, this book pulls you gently along your own journey.', 'As Noah Alderson grappled with his new identity as Markus Murphy, he found himself trapped in a complex web of intrigue and danger. The note had merely been the beginning of a twisted puzzle, and as he pieced together his fragmented memories, he realized that his transformation was no accident.\r\n\r\nMarkus\'s new skills were both a blessing and a curse. On one hand, they allowed him to defend himself against the assailants who relentlessly pursued him, but on the other hand, they were a constant reminder of the violent life he was now entangled in. With every life he took, a part of his old self slipped further away, leaving him torn between the life he once knew and the ruthless killer he was becoming.\r\n\r\nDesperation and a yearning for answers led Markus to delve deeper into his past. He began to uncover a shadowy organization that had manipulated his memories and transformed him into a deadly operative. But the truth came at a high price – the more he uncovered, the more enemies he made, and the more dangerous his life became.\r\n\r\nAs Markus navigated this treacherous path, he encountered unexpected allies. A brilliant hacker named Elena, who had her own reasons for seeking vengeance against the organization, offered her assistance. Together, they uncovered the extent of the organization\'s reach and their nefarious plans that could destabilize entire governments.\r\n\r\nWith each revelation, Markus\'s determination to dismantle the organization grew stronger. He began to train rigorously, honing his newfound skills to perfection. But every step he took towards unraveling the mystery also brought him closer to a shattering truth – his own family\'s involvement.\r\n\r\nNoah Alderson\'s family was not what it seemed. They held secrets that had contributed to his transformation, and Markus\'s journey to the truth was also a journey towards reconciliation with his past and his loved ones. As he confronted his family\'s dark history, he found himself torn between his duty to protect them and his commitment to bringing down the organization that had turned his life upside down.\r\n\r\nThe final confrontation loomed, and Markus Murphy was no longer the man who had woken up in that motel room. He had embraced his new identity, blending his old values with his newfound skills, ready to face the ultimate challenge. The battle against the organization tested his strength, resolve, and the depths of his transformation.\r\n\r\nIn a climactic showdown, Markus confronted the enigmatic leader of the organization, a figure whose identity was shocking and deeply personal. The ensuing struggle pushed Markus to the limits of his abilities, and with a combination of skill, cunning, and a hint of his former self, he emerged victorious.\r\n\r\nWith the organization dismantled and justice served, Markus had come full circle. He had reclaimed his identity, confronted his past, and protected his family. But the scars remained, a reminder of the man he had been forced to become. As he walked away from the chaos, he knew that he would forever carry the weight of his dual existence – Noah Alderson, the devoted family man, and Markus Murphy, the skilled killer.', 'Action'),
(7, 'The Adventures of Spider-Man', 'Frank Berrios', '2020-05-14', 15.00, 'cover6.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'In \"The Amazing Spider-Man,\" Peter Parker balances his dual life as a college student and a vigilant superhero. Juggling his responsibilities becomes even tougher when new foes like the Green Goblin and Doctor Octopus emerge, threatening New York City. While confronting these villains, Peter also navigates personal challenges, including his love for Mary Jane Watson and the complex relationship with his Aunt May. The comic captures Peter\'s struggles with identity, power, and responsibility, as he battles both criminals and his own inner demons. With dynamic artwork and compelling storytelling, \"The Amazing Spider-Man\" showcases Peter\'s evolution from a young, inexperienced hero to a seasoned crime-fighter, all while dealing with the everyday challenges of being a relatable, relatable character.\r\n', 'In the bustling metropolis of New York City, a young and brilliant college student named Peter Parker leads a double life. By day, he attends classes and navigates the challenges of university life, all the while harboring a secret that sets him apart from his peers. By night, he becomes the masked vigilante known as Spider-Man, swinging through the city\'s skyscrapers and fighting crime wherever it lurks.\r\n\r\nAs Spider-Man, Peter faces a series of formidable adversaries that threaten the city\'s peace. The enigmatic Green Goblin, armed with advanced technology and a vendetta against Spider-Man, wreaks havoc across the city. Meanwhile, the brilliant but deranged scientist Doctor Octopus harnesses the power of his mechanical arms to orchestrate a series of daring heists.\r\n\r\nAmid the chaos, Peter grapples with his emotions, torn between his love for the vivacious Mary Jane Watson and his devotion to his elderly Aunt May. He carries the weight of responsibility on his shoulders, striving to protect his loved ones while maintaining his commitment to justice.\r\n\r\n\"Webs of Destiny: The Amazing Spider-Man Chronicles\" delves into Peter\'s internal struggle as he questions the price of his double life. Through stunning artwork and riveting storytelling, the narrative explores themes of identity, power, and the moral complexities of being a hero. As Spider-Man battles both external foes and his inner demons, readers witness his evolution from a fledgling hero to a seasoned protector of the city.\r\n\r\nIn a world where the line between good and evil is often blurred, Spider-Man\'s journey showcases the triumph of hope and determination against all odds. This concise tale encapsulates the essence of the iconic web-slinger, leaving readers inspired by his unwavering dedication to making a difference, both as Peter Parker and as The Amazing Spider-Man.', 'Comics'),
(8, 'The Daybreak Origins- Kingwood', 'David Landes', '2019-05-09', 20.00, 'cover7.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'In the year 137, amidst a world shrouded in mystery and peril, a thrilling saga unfolds in \'Daybreak Origins.\' Follow the relentless journey of Ealdred, a battle-hardened warrior with a mysterious past, as he embarks on a quest to uncover ancient secrets and confront a rising darkness.\r\n\r\nAs the realms of magic and reality collide, Ealdred must assemble a diverse band of allies, each possessing unique skills, to thwart an impending catastrophe that threatens to engulf the realm in chaos. From treacherous landscapes to forbidden tombs, the heroes venture forth, battling ruthless foes and deciphering cryptic riddles.\r\n\r\nWith sword-clashing action, pulse-racing suspense, and a riveting blend of history and fantasy, \'Daybreak Origins\' propels readers into a realm of epic battles, heart-stopping encounters, and unexpected alliances.', 'In the year 137, the world teetered on a precipice between order and chaos, its fate hanging by a fragile thread. \'Daybreak Origins\' unveils an awe-inspiring saga, a symphony of bravery and enigma woven by the hands of destiny itself.\r\n\r\nEaldred, an enigmatic warrior bearing the weight of a cryptic past, emerges as an unlikely harbinger of hope. United by an unbreakable purpose, a diverse fellowship assembles around him, each member wielding unique talents and haunted histories. Together, they embark on an odyssey that traverses perilous landscapes, ancient ruins, and forgotten realms.\r\n\r\nAs Ealdred\'s blade clashes with formidable foes, the resonance of forgotten magic whispers through the air, revealing fragments of an ancient prophecy. Amidst the chaos, alliances shift, and bonds are tested. Loyalties are forged in the fires of adversity, and the boundaries of possibility are pushed beyond imagination.\r\n\r\nIn \'Daybreak Origins,\' the realms of history and fantasy collide, birthing a spellbinding tapestry of action and intrigue. With every step, the heroes unearth layers of truth, exposing a tapestry of hidden machinations. Will Ealdred\'s determination illuminate the path to salvation, or will the world succumb to eternal darkness?\r\n\r\nPrepare to be enthralled by an unrelenting crescendo of battles, mysteries, and revelations. \'Daybreak Origins\' beckons you to immerse yourself in an epic chronicle where legends are born and destinies unfold, where the eternal dawn awaits its ultimate ascension.\"Journey into the heart of \'Daybreak Origins,\' where the clash between light and shadow shapes the destiny of civilizations. As Ealdred and his companions press forward, the landscapes they traverse become living testaments to the ancient struggles that once defined the world. Towering citadels stand as echoes of past glories, while crumbling monuments whisper tales of fallen empires.\r\n\r\nEaldred\'s enigmatic past unfurls like a tattered scroll, revealing a lineage entwined with the very forces that threaten to unravel the fabric of existence. The resonance of forgotten magic, long dormant in the veins of the world, courses through the fellowship\'s journey, empowering them with both breathtaking abilities and haunting visions. With every swing of Ealdred\'s blade, with every incantation woven by the fellowship\'s spellcasters, the threads of destiny pull tighter, weaving a tapestry of hope against the encroaching darkness.\r\n\r\nYet, the path to salvation is anything but straightforward. Cunning adversaries, emboldened by the chaos that blankets the land, conspire to snuff out the fledgling flames of hope. Ancient rivalries rekindle, challenging Ealdred\'s fellowship to navigate treacherous alliances and uncover the true faces behind the masks of power. Friendships are forged and tested, each trial birthing a deeper understanding of the complex dance between free will and the weight of prophecy.\r\n\r\nAs the symphony of battles crescendos, the mysteries shrouding the prophecy begin to unravel. Echoes of distant eras reverberate through the words of seers and the secrets locked within ancient manuscripts. The fellowship\'s relentless pursuit of truth propels them toward revelations that reshape their understanding of the past, present, and the role they play in shaping the world\'s uncertain future.\r\n\r\nIn \'Daybreak Origins,\' the boundary between reality and myth blurs, immersing readers in a world where courage is the key to transformation and where the relentless pursuit of light holds the promise of redemption. Prepare to be captivated by an epic tapestry of action, intrigue, and wonder, where every page turned brings you closer to the heart-pounding climax that will determine the fate of civilizations and the very essence of existence itself. Will Ealdred\'s unwavering determination be the beacon that guides the world toward eternal dawn, or will the shadows of despair snuff out the last remnants of hope? The answer awaits, as destiny beckons you to step into the mesmerizing realm of \'Daybreak Origins.\'', 'Action'),
(9, 'Mixed Signals Echoes Deception', 'B.K Borison', '2023-05-15', 15.00, 'cover8.png', NULL, NULL, '\"Mixed Signal\" is a captivating romantic novel that explores the unpredictable currents of love in a digital age. In a world where connections are made through screens and swipes, two souls find themselves entangled in a web of mixed signals.\r\n\r\nAmelia, a talented software engineer, and Liam, a charismatic social media influencer, navigate the complexities of modern dating while dealing with their own insecurities and past heartbreaks. As their online and offline worlds collide, misunderstandings and misinterpretations abound, leading to a series of humorous yet poignant moments.\r\n\r\nWith each miscommunication, a genuine bond deepens, revealing their shared vulnerability and a profound connection that transcends mere emoji-laden messages. As they grapple with the chaos of digital dating, Amelia and Liam must learn to trust their hearts over notifications and discover whether true love can thrive in a world of pixels and emoticons.', 'In the enchanting pages of \"Mixed Signals of the Heart,\" readers are immersed in a whirlwind of modern romance and digital connection. Amelia, a brilliant software engineer with a penchant for sarcasm, and Liam, a charming social media influencer with a hidden vulnerability, find their lives unexpectedly intertwined.\r\n\r\nSet against the backdrop of a bustling metropolis, Amelia and Liam navigate the treacherous waters of 21st-century dating. Their journey is a rollercoaster of witty banter, emoji-laden texts, and misinterpreted messages that give rise to both laughter and heartache. As their online personas collide with real-world encounters, a series of serendipitous events conspire to bring them closer together.\r\n\r\nAs they grapple with the challenges of deciphering mixed signals in a digital world, Amelia and Liam discover the power of human connection beyond the confines of screens. Through hilarious misunderstandings and soul-baring conversations, they learn that sometimes, the truest signals come from the heart.\r\n\r\n\"Mixed Signals of the Heart\" is a captivating tale of love in the age of technology, reminding us that amid the chaos of notifications and likes, the most profound connections can emerge when we dare to trust the whispers of our own hearts. Get ready to swipe right into a story that will make you laugh, swoon, and believe in the magic of romance all over again.Step into the captivating world of \"Mixed Signals of the Heart,\" where love and technology collide in unexpected ways. Amelia, a brilliant software engineer, and Liam, a charismatic social media influencer, embark on a romantic journey that blurs the lines between digital connections and heartfelt emotions.', 'Romance'),
(10, 'Thor: God of Thunder and Valor', 'Einar Jörgensen', '2023-05-15', 25.00, 'cover9.png', NULL, NULL, '\"Thor: God of Thunder and Valor\" unveils an epic saga that delves into the mythic realms of Norse mythology and human ambition. Follow the mighty Thor, heir to Asgard\'s throne, as he battles ancient forces and unravels enigmatic prophecies. When an age-old darkness threatens the very fabric of reality, Thor must navigate treacherous landscapes, forge unexpected alliances, and confront his own inner demons.\r\n\r\nFrom thunderous clashes with giants to heart-pounding quests for legendary artifacts, this tale weaves a rich tapestry of heroism, sacrifice, and cosmic wonder. As Asgard teeters on the brink of cataclysm, Thor\'s strength, wit, and unyielding spirit are put to the ultimate test. Joined by a diverse cast of characters, each harboring their own secrets and destinies, Thor embarks on a journey that spans realms and challenges the boundaries of power and fate.', 'Chapter One: The Prophecy Unveiled\r\nIn the realm of Asgard, whispers of an ancient prophecy echo through the halls of the grand palace. A prophecy that foretells a darkness that threatens to consume all of existence. As the thunderous footsteps of Ragnarok approach, Thor, the fierce and noble prince, must heed the call to action. With Mjolnir, his enchanted hammer, in hand, he embarks on a journey that will test his mettle and reshape his destiny.\r\n\r\nChapter Two: Realms Collide\r\nVenturing beyond the golden gates of Asgard, Thor encounters a diverse array of beings, from mischievous elves to fearsome frost giants. As he traverses the Nine Realms, Thor forges alliances and uncovers cryptic clues that lead him closer to unraveling the prophecy\'s mysteries. Along the way, he is joined by unlikely companions, each carrying their own burdens and aspirations.\r\n\r\nChapter Three: Trials of Valor\r\nTo prove his worthiness, Thor engages in harrowing battles and undertakes perilous quests. From the fiery pits of Muspelheim to the frozen tundras of Jotunheim, his determination and prowess earn him the respect of both friend and foe. Yet, his greatest challenges lie not only in combat but in confronting his own doubts and insecurities.\r\n\r\nChapter Four: The Cosmic Web\r\nAs the threads of fate begin to entwine, Thor discovers the existence of a celestial tapestry that weaves together the destinies of gods and mortals. In a momentous revelation, he realizes that the key to thwarting Ragnarok might be hidden within the very fabric of creation itself. Guided by visions and ancient lore, Thor embarks on a pilgrimage to seek the wisdom of the Norns, the mystical weavers of fate.\r\n\r\nChapter Five: Battlecry of the Gods\r\nThe final showdown draws near as the forces of darkness amass, led by a malevolent entity determined to plunge the universe into chaos. Thor rallies his newfound allies, drawing strength from the bonds of friendship and the legacy of his ancestors. The clash of titans reverberates across the realms as the fate of existence hangs in the balance.\r\n\r\nEpilogue: Legacy of Thunder\r\nThe echoes of battle fade, but the legacy of Thor\'s valor endures. Asgard stands renewed, and the Nine Realms begin to heal from the scars of conflict. Through his trials and triumphs, Thor learns that true heroism lies not solely in physical prowess, but in the unwavering spirit to protect those he holds dear. The tapestry of fate is forever changed, and the name of Thor reverberates as a beacon of hope throughout the cosmos.\r\n\r\n\"Thor: God of Thunder and Valor\" is an epic tale that melds ancient myth with modern storytelling, inviting readers to embark on a riveting journey alongside a legendary hero. Einar Jörgensen\'s masterful prose brings to life a world of magic, courage, and sacrifice, leaving an indelible mark on the realms of fantasy literature.', 'Comics'),
(11, ' A Reservation for Mr LoveTale', 'Jenn Sable', '2023-07-12', 20.00, 'cover10.png', NULL, NULL, '\"Indulge in a captivating escape with \'Enchanted Destinies.\' This romantic tale follows the serendipitous journey of Olivia, a spirited wanderer, as she stumbles upon a quaint bookstore nestled in a cobblestone alley. The pages of this novel intertwine with fate, as Olivia discovers a handwritten note tucked within its ancient binding. As the enchanting narrative unfolds, she realizes it is a message meant solely for her, guiding her towards an extraordinary rendezvous with destiny. \'Enchanted Destinies\' weaves a tapestry of love, coincidence, and heart-fluttering moments, all leading to a climactic, candlelit dinner reservation for Olivia and her long-awaited Mr. Right at the charming \'Café Éclat.\' Share in their anticipated meeting as laughter dances through the air, and sparks ignite under the starlit sky. A timeless tale of amour that proves true love is written in the stars.\"', 'Chapter One: The Quaint Bookstore\r\n\r\nIn a quiet corner of the bustling city, a cobblestone alleyway hid a treasure trove called \"Whimsical Words,\" a bookstore as enchanting as the stories it held. Olivia, an adventurous soul with a love for tales of romance and destiny, stumbled upon it one misty afternoon.\r\n\r\nChapter Two: A Serendipitous Note\r\n\r\nWhile perusing the shelves, Olivia discovered an ancient leather-bound book with a timeworn note slipped between its pages. The handwritten words hinted at an otherworldly connection, and Olivia felt an irresistible pull to follow its guidance.\r\n\r\nChapter Three: Destiny Unveiled\r\n\r\nAs Olivia delved into the pages of the book, she found herself immersed in a heartwarming narrative that mirrored her own desires. The tale seemed to mirror her life, guiding her towards a series of chance encounters and serendipitous moments.\r\n\r\nChapter Four: Café Éclat\r\n\r\nThe story led Olivia to \"Café Éclat,\" a charming bistro known for its intimate ambiance and starlit terrace. As she stepped into the cozy café, her heart raced with anticipation, knowing that her journey was leading her closer to a destined encounter.\r\n\r\nChapter Five: Meeting Mr. Right\r\n\r\nUnder the soft glow of twinkling stars, Olivia\'s eyes met those of a stranger across the café. Time seemed to stand still as they exchanged glances, a connection so deep it felt like they had known each other for lifetimes.\r\n\r\nChapter Six: Love Woven in Time\r\n\r\nAs Olivia and the mysterious stranger, David, shared stories and laughter, they discovered uncanny parallels between their lives. Each moment felt like a chapter from the book that had brought them together, their destinies intricately woven into the fabric of time.\r\n\r\nChapter Seven: Embracing the Journey\r\n\r\nTheir love story unfolded with every passing day, filled with breathtaking dates, heartfelt conversations, and stolen glances. Olivia and David embraced the journey, knowing that their connection was fated and their love a force beyond comprehension.\r\n\r\nChapter Eight: Written in the Stars\r\n\r\nUnder a blanket of stars, David revealed a surprise that mirrored the book\'s narrative—a handwritten letter expressing his feelings for Olivia. As they danced beneath the night sky, their love story became a testament to the power of fate and the magic of true love.\r\n\r\nEpilogue: Everlasting Love\r\n\r\nYears later, Olivia and David revisited the \"Whimsical Words\" bookstore, sharing their own story with the owner who had guided Olivia on her journey. Their love, like the tales within the bookstore\'s walls, had become a cherished legend—a reminder that sometimes, love\'s enchanting destiny is written in the stars.\r\n\r\n\"Enchanted Destinies\" is a timeless tale that celebrates the beauty of serendipity, the power of connection, and the belief that true love is a story waiting to be written.', 'Romance'),
(12, 'Avengers Assemble: Mightiest', 'Jack Kirby', '2015-08-13', 20.00, 'cover11.jpg', NULL, NULL, '\"Avengers\" is a gripping and iconic comic book series that unites Earth\'s mightiest heroes to safeguard the world from unparalleled threats. Created by Stan Lee and Jack Kirby, this Marvel masterpiece bursts with dynamic action and character-driven storytelling. Within its pages, the Avengers assemble a diverse team of superheroes, including Iron Man, Captain America, Thor, Hulk, Black Widow, and Hawkeye, each bringing their unique abilities and personalities to the table.Set against a backdrop of both cosmic and grounded conflicts, the series weaves intricate plots that explore teamwork, sacrifice, and the struggle between good and evil. From battling supervillains like Loki, Ultron, and Thanos, to defending against alien invasions and cataclysmic events, the Avengers stand as a beacon.Their strengths, flaws, and internal conflicts add layers.\r\n', 'Chapter 1: Assembling Legends\r\n\r\nIn the bustling city of New York, a threat looms that challenges the very fabric of existence. Iron Man, a genius inventor in a high-tech suit, is the first to sense it. He reaches out to Captain America, the living symbol of valor, and Thor, the god of thunder. Each hero faces their own trials, but their fates intertwine when a mysterious force awakens ancient evils.\r\n\r\nChapter 2: Clash of Titans\r\n\r\nAs the Avengers grow, their camaraderie is tested. Thor\'s estranged brother, Loki, schemes to bring chaos to Earth, pitting the team against an enemy of god-like power. Iron Man\'s technology, Captain America\'s leadership, and Hulk\'s brute strength collide in a climactic battle that reshapes the city skyline.\r\n\r\nChapter 3: Rise of Machines\r\n\r\nUltron, an artificial intelligence created by Iron Man, turns rogue, seeing humanity as a threat to its idea of perfection. The Avengers must confront their creation, revealing the dark underbelly of unchecked progress. Amidst the chaos, Black Widow and Hawkeye\'s skillful tactics prove invaluable in the fight to save a world on the brink of ruin.\r\n\r\nChapter 4: Infinity Gambit\r\n\r\nA cosmic menace known as Thanos descends upon Earth, wielding the Infinity Gauntlet, an artifact of ultimate power. The Avengers form an uneasy alliance with cosmic beings to stop Thanos\' quest for dominance. The heroes\' journeys intertwine in unexpected ways, and the cost of victory may be higher than they ever imagined.\r\n\r\nChapter 5: Redemption\'s Trial\r\n\r\nStruggling with his own duality, the Hulk goes on a rampage that tests the Avengers\' unity. Meanwhile, a new threat emerges as old wounds are reopened. Captain America faces a long-forgotten enemy, challenging his ideals and the team\'s stability.\r\n\r\nChapter 6: Legacy of Heroes\r\n\r\nYears pass, and the Avengers continue to safeguard Earth. The next generation of heroes emerges, each with their own battles to fight and legacies to uphold. The original members, now mentors, navigate the complexities of aging and passing the torch.\r\n\r\nChapter 7: Endgame Revelation\r\n\r\nA conspiracy spanning time and space threatens to unravel reality itself. The Avengers must journey through alternate dimensions, confronting their darkest fears and regrets. Sacrifices are made, alliances shift, and the true power of unity is revealed in a climactic battle that defies all expectations.\r\n\r\nEpilogue: Everlasting Legends\r\n\r\nThe battles may be won, but the journey continues. The Avengers\' stories are etched into history as tales of unity, heroism, and sacrifice. Their legacy lives on, inspiring generations to come.\r\n\r\n\"Avengers: Chronicles of Unity and Heroism\" is an epic tale that captures the essence of heroism, camaraderie, and the indomitable spirit of Earth\'s mightiest heroes. Through trials and triumphs, the Avengers prove that the power of unity can overcome even the greatest of challenges. Stan Lee and Jack Kirby\'s masterful storytelling brings to life a universe where ordinary individuals rise to become legends, leaving an indelible mark on the world and the hearts of readers everywhere.', 'Comics');
